data.description: Upon entering this stunning home, you are greeted with a high vault ceiling, and separate living and dining rooms.  This gorgeous three side brick home features 4 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and 4 fireplaces. The main level consists of a spacious family room perfect for entertaining, with a cozy fireplace, and a breakfast area with a stunning view into the eat-in kitchen. You will enjoy preparing your favorite meals in this kitchen as it's fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a pantry, and easy access to your deck. The basement is partially finished, allowing for additional living space and endless possibilities.
